      "concept": "Vocab — Greeting + Reply",
      "en": [
        "Greeting: 'How are you?' (informal)",
        "Give the typical Greek back-and-forth."
      ],
      "gr": [
        "1. Ti kaneis?",
        "2. Kala, esy?",
        "3. Kala, efharisto."
